snippet.title: Ultra Custom Night - Trailer 3
snippet.description:
Play the game here: https://gamejolt.com/games/ultracustomnight/497721 (what is revealed in the trailer is not currently in the released build!)

The trailer was originally revealed at the Fangames at Freddy's Summer Showcase event: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T4U59etvIY8&

Trailer edited by CircusRama, with additional clips provided by Yendo (@PokeySnow). Totem Panic in the intro is voiced by Chimin (@Chimin395).
